{"serial": "00114", "department_serial": 4, "code": "LN7002", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Introduction to Teaching Chinese as a Second or Foreign Language", "ch": "華語文教學概論"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "華語文教學學分學必修課程。"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Li, Ming-Yi"], "ch": ["李明懿"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["9", "A", "B"]}, "loc": {"building": "O", "room": "312"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "語言中心", "en": "Language Center"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 24, "remark": {"ch": "華語文教學學分學必修課程。", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程是華語教學的入門課程，也是華語教學學程「教學三部曲」的第一部。課程將帶領同學探知華語教學的專業概況和基礎專業知識。", "en": "This course is an introductory course in “ Teaching Chinese as a 2nd/ foreign language“. The course will guide students to explore the professional overview and basic professional knowledge of Chinese language teaching."}, "outline": {"ch": "學生將在本課程中：\n1. 知悉華語文教育的特性、現況、發展脈絡和未來趨勢。\n2. 認識華語文教學內容(語音、詞彙、語法、漢字)的語言特性。\n3. 初探華語文聽說讀寫文化教學的課程特性、目標和教學操作。\n4. 認識現今華語教學等級大綱的模式和原則。\n5. 探討數位科技應用於華語文教學的現況和未來。\n6. 掌握華語教學常用的拼音系統。", "en": "In this course, students are expected to:\n1. Understand the characteristics, current status, development context, and future trends of Chinese language education.\n2. Recognize the linguistic characteristics\nof Chinese language teaching content (phonetics, vocabulary, grammar, Chinese characters).\n3. Explore the course characteristics, goals, and teaching operations of listening, speaking, reading, writing, and cultural teaching in Chinese.\n4. Observe the current guidelines of curriculum and proficiency benchmark in TCSL.\n5. Discuss the current status and future of application of digital technology in Chinese language teaching.\n6. Master the commonly used pinyin systems in Chinese language teaching."}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. H. D. Brown (2014/ 6th edition) Principle of Language Teaching and Teaching. New York: Pearson. (中譯2016版) \n2. 何淑貞等（2019）華語文教學導論(第二版)。 台北：三民。\n1. H. D. Brown (2014/ 6th edition) Principle of Language Teaching and Teaching. New York: Pearson. (中譯2016版)", "en": "1. H. D. Brown (2014/ 6th edition) Principle of Language Teaching and Teaching. New York: Pearson. (中譯2016版) \n2. 何淑貞等（2019）華語文教學導論(第二版)。 台北：三民。\n1. H. D. Brown (2014/ 6th edition) Principle of Language Teaching and Teaching. New York: Pearson. (中譯2016版)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30%", "en": "30%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n個別指導\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "Individual Instruction", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "課程參與60％\n出席狀況 (10％)\n課堂表現 (30％)\n作業 (20％)\n期末報告40％\n 課堂表現: 以聽講、發言、與其他同學互動及合作之表現為主。", "en": "Course participation 60％\nAttendance status (10％)\nClassroom performance (30％)\nHomework (20％)\nFinal report 40％\n\n#Classroom performance: Focus on listening, discussing, interacting, and cooperating with other students."}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週二三四 11:00-12:00", "en": "11:00-12:00 Tuesday, Wednesday, and Thursday"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "本課程課堂上課16週，另安排課堂上課以外的時間進行課堂外學習活動，如聆聽演講、參與工作坊或校外參訪。課程將於12月25日結束。", "en": "This course lasts for 16 weeks in class, and individual tutoring and off-class academic activities will be arranged outside of class time. Courses will end on December 25th."}, "domain": {"ch": "華語教學", "en": "華語教學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言溝通", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "文化視野", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "自主學習", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Language & Communication Skills", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance", "S